Class Feature

java.lang.Object
  package2.Feature
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
public class Feature
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable

Feature class for MoleculeDNA. Contains type (String), name (String[2]), and Position of a single Feature. If Feature is a Protein-coding segment add also proteinProduct. A note (String) and additionalInfo can also be added. Everything is added using the constructor.

Author:
kingcarlxx
